<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, July 16 (Xinhua) -- The index of Tunis Exchange closed
at 454.10 points on Thursday, dropping 0.94 points from that of
Wednesday's close.
