entertained Chinese classical music lovers with the Festival
Variations and the Year of the Dragon and other classical pieces
in its premiere.
</P>
<P>
The performance, together with the Military Band of the Chinese
People's Liberation Army (PLA), is designed to mark the 71st
anniversary of the founding of the PLA.
</P>
<P>
