the Australian band is a highly skillful band, and that the
co-performance on the same stage not only is good for us to learn
from each other, but also is beneficial to promoting exchanges
between the two armies.
</P>
<P>
Wang Guangying, vice-chairman of the National People's Congress
(NPC) Standing Committee, and other senior Chinese officials
were among the Chinese music lovers tonight.
</P>
<P>
The Australian army band is here at the invitation of the
Chinese People's Association for Friendship with Foreign
Countries.  
