<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 17 (Xinhua) -- The All-China Federation of Trade
Unions today called on trade unions across the nation to help
laid-off workers find new jobs and ensure basic living standards.
</P>
<P>
Federation president Zhang Dinghua said that all the local
trade unions should place priority on assisting laid-off workers,
extend the greatest possible efforts to train 1.5 million
