<HEADLINE> Jiang Zemin on Study of Deng Xiaoping Theory </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 17 (Xinhua) -- Jiang Zemin, general secretary of
the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China (CPC), said
today that further studies of Deng Xiaoping Theory must be carried
out in line with the study of the guidelines of the 15th National
Congress of the Communist Party of China.
</P>
<P>
Related studies will enable people to gain a comprehensive and
correct understanding of Deng Xiaoping Theory and wholeheartedly
proceed with the cause of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics in the 21st century, said Jiang.
</P>
<P>
Jiang made the remarks during a speech to a work conference on
the study of Deng Xiaoping Theory which began in Beijing today.
</P>
<P>
He said that Deng Xiaoping Theory enabled China to record
remarkable achievements in reform and opening-up over the past two
decades, and fulfillment of the tasks set forth at the 15th
National Party Congress must rely on the guidance from the theory.
</P>
<P>
Facts have shown that the new progress China has made in the
economic, political and cultural fields and diplomatic work as
well since the 15th National Party Congress resulted from the
earnest implementation of Deng Xiaoping Theory, said Jiang.
</P>
<P>
He said that qualified leaders must consistently study and
practice Deng Xiaoping Theory, stressing that it will otherwise be
impossible to correctly carry out Party policies since building
socialism with Chinese characteristics is an unprecedented
undertaking.
</P>
<P>
He stressed people must study the theory in their spare time,
and must never be satisfied with a minimal understanding or
otherwise engage in formalism, which might in any way damage the
Party or the country.
</P>
<P>
Leading officials at all levels must assume full responsibility
for organizing study groups and providing people, leading
officials in particular, with a full understanding of Deng
Xiaoping Theory, said Jiang.
</P>
<P>
The media in Beijing has answered Jiang's call by making full
preparations to publicize Deng Xiaoping Theory, while the
Organization and Publicity Departments of the CPC Central Committee
has issued a circular calling for all Party members to study
Deng Xiaoping Theory.
</P>
<P>
Hu Jintao, Wei Jianxing and Li Lanqing, members of the Standing
Committee of the Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee,
and other senior Party officials attended today's session of the
work conference. 
</P>
</TEXT>
