<HEADLINE> Light Rail Construction Firm Established </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, July 17 (Xinhua) -- The Shanghai Urban Light Rail
Communications and Construction Co., the first of its kind in
China, was established in Shanghai on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The venture was established by six companies, including the
Shanghai Subway Corp., Shanghai Urban Construction Co. and
Shanghai Tunnel Engineering Holding Co.
</P>
<P>
The goal of the company, established with the approval of the
State Development Planning Commission and the Ministry of
Construction, is to improve urban traffic in large cities.
</P>
<P>
Light rail traffic is expected to play an increasingly
important role in easing urban traffic congestion and improving
urban environment.
</P>
<P>
Various cities, including Zhuhai, Shenzhen, Nanjing, Qingdao
and Chongqing Municipality, are currently planning to build local
systems.
</P>
<P>
The new company will not only play a positive role in
developing rail transport in Shanghai and China as a whole, but
will also help to avoid construction redundancies.  
</P>
</TEXT>
