agreement reached between Yugoslav President Slobodan Milosevic
and Russian President Boris Yeltsin in their Moscow meeting in
June.
</P>
<P>
He said that Yugoslavia, generally speaking, is honoring the
promise Milosevic made during his visit to Moscow and the ball is
on the court of the ethnic Albanians in Kosovo, a province of
Serbia. 
