yesterday to "concentrate on major problems" and "continue the
ongoing battle against serious crimes."
</P>
<P>
-- China repeated its criticism yesterday of U.S. congressmen
who "stirred up trouble" over the alleged transfer of satellite
technology to China.
</P>
<P>
China and the United States have cooperated in launching
satellites in normal bilateral commercial exchanges, said Foreign
Ministry spokesman Tang Guoqiang in Beijing yesterday.  
