<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS -- The Security Council of the United Nations on
Thursday approved the establishment of a program to monitor and
assess the court system in Bosnia as part of an overall program of
legal reform outlined by the Office of the High Representative for
the Peace Agreement on Bosnia and Herzegovina.
</P>
<P>
